flowchart LR
  User[User Browser]
  R53[Route 53 + ACM]
  CF[CloudFront + WAF]
  S3[S3 Frontend Bucket]
  ALB[Application Load Balancer]
  ECS[ECS Java Backend Service]
  Proxy[RDS Proxy]
  Aurora[Aurora Cluster]
  Logs[CloudWatch Logs]
  Traces[X-Ray / OTLP Trace Backend]
  Artifacts[S3 Evidence Artifacts]
  GUI[JavaFX Desktop GUI]

  User --> R53 --> CF
  CF -->|static assets| S3
  CF -->|/api/*| ALB --> ECS --> Proxy --> Aurora
  ECS --> Logs
  ECS --> Traces
  ECS --> Artifacts
  ALB --> Artifacts
  CF --> Artifacts
  GUI --> Logs
  GUI --> Traces
  GUI --> Artifacts
  GUI --> Aurora
